name: Morondanga Republik: Marla Reliquia Cerezo, president (1945-1949)
description: Marla Reliquia Cerezo was the president of Morondanga Republik in the period 1945-1949.Before that she dedicated herself to beekeeping with love and patience, virtues that also accompanied her throughout her political career.  Marla had a Siamese twin sister. She was not included in the stamp.
